<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.3">
<l>īvi lāta tīviṉaika ḷettaṉai ceyta ṉaṉkol</l>
<l>tāvi vaiyaṅ koṇṭa ventāy tāmōtarā veṉṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>kūvik kūvi neñcurukik kaṇpaṉi cōra niṉṟāl</l>
<l>pāvi nīyeṉ ṟoṉṟu collāy pāviyēṉ kāṇavantē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How many actions that are without charity have I committed?</l>
<l>If, saying [nd] saying “my father who expanded [and] took the world, Tāmotara”,</l>
<l>calling [and] calling, [my] heart melting I stand while tears trickle from [my] eyes,</l>
<l>won’t you say one thing “you wretch”, caming so that wretched I can see [you]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
